Definition: an event resulting in great loss and misfortune
Example: the whole city was affected by the irremediable calamity; the earthquake was a disaster
Synonyms: adj, all, unfortunate, calamitous, catastrophe, disaster, disastrous, tragedy, sad, tragical, tragic, cataclysm, destructive, cataclysmic, cataclysmal, misfortune, an, event, resulting, in, great, loss, and, the, whole, city, was, affected, by, irremediable, earthquake, a
Category: noun.event
